{
  "text": "Fecal fat content of the rats were determined based on the slightly modified method described by [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Briefly, feces (0.5 g) were soaked in 2 mL distilled water and homogenized completely. It was then stored at 4\u00b0C for 24 h followed by homogenization by vortex for 1 min. Extraction of lipids from feces was executed using 7.5 mL chloroform : methanol (1:2, v:v) for 30 min, followed by the addition of 2.5 mL of chloroform and deionized water and shaking for another 30 min. Resultant mixtures were then centrifuged (at 2000 \u00d7 g) for 15 min, the lipophilic layer was isolated and dried under vacuum.",
  "correct_citation": {
